OL,3,C'We lost everything': Fundao Dam burst
OL,4,Csurvivors are fighting for justice
OL,6,FBHP and Vale will be put on trial in
OL,7,FLondon to see what role they played in
OL,8,Fone of Brazil's worst environmental
OL,9,Fdisasters. Rachel Townsend visited the
OL,10,Fcountry to explore the aftermath
OL,12,F"We lost everything because of greed.
OL,13,FWhat won't a person do for money?"
OL,15,FThis is the question being asked by
OL,16,Fformer residents of Bento Rodrigues.
OL,18,FFormer residents, because the village
OL,19,Fno longer exists.
