OL,3,C'We lost everything': Fundao Dam burst
OL,4,Csurvivors are fighting for justice
OL,6,FAs part of a team from On Assignment,
OL,7,Fwe travelled to the state of Minas
OL,8,FGerais, in southern Brazil, to speak
OL,9,Fto the people whose lives were torn
OL,10,Fapart by one of the country's worst
OL,11,Fenvironmental disasters. It is clear
OL,12,Fwho they blame.
OL,14,FOn the afternoon of November 5, 2015,
OL,15,Fthose living in Bento Rodrigues
OL,16,Fdescribed a darkness descending on the
OL,17,Fvillage. They knew instantly what had
OL,18,Fhappened.
