OL,3,C'We lost everything': Fundao Dam burst
OL,4,Csurvivors are fighting for justice
OL,6,FThe Fundao Dam had burst, releasing
OL,7,Fmillions of litres of contaminated
OL,8,Fwaste, headed directly for Bento. In
OL,9,Fminutes, the village was turned to
OL,10,Frubble. People knew if they didn't
OL,11,Fescape, the mudslide would kill them.
OL,13,FThe iron ore mine was run operated by
OL,14,FSamarco, along with their parent
OL,15,Fcompanies Vale and BHP, which is
OL,16,Fpartly British owned.
