OL,3,C'We lost everything': Fundao Dam burst
OL,4,Csurvivors are fighting for justice
OL,6,FPamela was leaving college when news
OL,7,Fof the dam burst reached her. She ran
OL,8,Fbarefoot towards the tsunami of waste,
OL,9,Fknowing that her husband and two
OL,10,Fchildren would be right in its path.
OL,12,FWhen she reached home, a neighbour
OL,13,Ftold her: "Everyone is dead".
