OL,3,C'We lost everything': Fundao Dam burst
OL,4,Csurvivors are fighting for justice
OL,6,F"My world collapsed and I sat there in
OL,7,Fthe middle of the street, where I was
OL,8,Fand there I cried. And people kept
OL,9,Fcoming with different news saying they
OL,10,Fhad found someone or that they had
OL,11,Fdied, full of uncertainty. So I
OL,12,Fdecided to go out to look and I went
OL,13,Fout and went down. And I shouted
OL,14,F'Manu, Nicolas!' and nothing."
