OL,3,C'We lost everything': Fundao Dam burst
OL,4,Csurvivors are fighting for justice
OL,6,FThe next day, Pamela was reunited with
OL,7,Fher son. He had clung to the inside of
OL,8,Fa car and survived. But her five-year-
OL,9,Fold daughter Manu was swept away and
OL,10,Fkilled. It was five days before Pamela
OL,11,Flearned what had happened.
OL,13,FSobbing as she spoke, Pamela said: "I
OL,14,Fspent five days without sleeping,
OL,15,Fwithout eating properly because there
OL,16,Fwas nothing about Manu. Everyone came
OL,17,Fand say they saw a girl like Manu in
OL,18,Fsuch a place and it left us even more
OL,19,Fin agony.
