OL,6,F"And then, they found my daughter on
OL,7,FGama's Bridge, a long way from here.
OL,8,FShe rolled in the mud for a long time.
OL,9,FAnd I have no idea what it was like
OL,10,Ffor her, you know. Her calling 'Mum,
OL,11,Fdad' and us not being there."
OL,13,FTragically, 19 people were killed;
OL,14,Famong them children and the elderly.
OL,16,FGelvana's seven-year-old son Thiago
OL,17,Fwas among them. In the moments before
OL,18,Fhe was swept away, he had clung
OL,19,Fdesperately to his grandmother. As the
OL,20,Favalanche hit, he was asking God to
OL,21,Fsave him.
