OL,6,FThiago's lifeless body was eventually
OL,7,Ffound 100 kilometres from Bento
OL,8,FRodrigues. Gelvana had been waiting
OL,9,Ffor news at a centre set up for
OL,10,Fsurvivors, in the nearby city of
OL,11,FMariana.
OL,13,F"Everyone was arriving and my son
OL,14,Fdidn't arrive. He didn't arrive and it
OL,15,Fwas like that, spending one day, two
OL,16,Fdays. I didn't eat, no drinking, no
OL,17,Fsleeping," she said.
