OL,3,C'We lost everything': Fundao Dam burst
OL,4,Csurvivors are fighting for justice
OL,6,F"I stayed seven days and seven nights
OL,7,Fwaiting for my son to arrive. And when
OL,8,Fseven days passed he didn't arrive.
OL,9,FUntil then my hope was that he was
OL,10,Fstill alive. And then the news came
OL,11,Fthat they had found his body 100
OL,12,Fkilometres away. And yet I didn't want
OL,13,Fto believe it. I arrived and the
OL,14,Fcoffin was sealed."
OL,16,FThiago was identified through his
OL,17,Fdental records.
