OL,3,C'We lost everything': Fundao Dam burst
OL,4,Csurvivors are fighting for justice
OL,6,F"That moment, I was already without
OL,7,Fstrength" Gelvana continued. "I
OL,8,Fcouldn't even walk. And that was when
OL,9,FI went to the cemetery. I arrived at
OL,10,Fthe cemetery and I couldn't see my
OL,11,Fson's little face. I couldn't say
OL,12,Fgoodbye. From that moment, my life was
OL,13,Fover."
OL,15,FAnd then a strength of will comes over
OL,16,FGelvana. A determination we hadn't
OL,17,Fseen before as she says: "And to this
OL,18,Fday I am fighting for justice".
OL,20,FThe justice she is talking about could
OL,21,Fbe handed down in the British courts.
