OL,3,C'We lost everything': Fundao Dam burst
OL,4,Csurvivors are fighting for justice
OL,6,FNext month, almost a decade after the
OL,7,Fdisaster, British law firm Pogust
OL,8,FGoodhead will lead a claim against the
OL,9,Fpartly British-owned parent company of
OL,10,FSamarco, BHP.
OL,12,FTheir goal is for the parent companies
OL,13,Fto take their share of responsibility
OL,14,Ffor the dam collapse.
OL,16,FBHP insists they already have. As a
OL,17,Fresult of the dam collapse, Samarco
OL,18,Fset up the Renova Foundation to manage
OL,19,Fcompensation to the victims of the
OL,20,Fdisaster.
