OL,6,FThey have compiled a $5 billion dollar
OL,7,F(#3.8 billion) package to build a new
OL,8,FBento Rodrigues which is almost
OL,9,Fcomplete. They say over $2 billion
OL,10,F(#1.5 billion) has been paid directly
OL,11,Fto more than 430,000 people. 450
OL,12,Fproperties have been rebuilt and 90%
OL,13,Fof resettlement cases have been
OL,14,Fcompleted.
