OL,3,C'We lost everything': Fundao Dam burst
OL,4,Csurvivors are fighting for justice
OL,6,FBut it is not just compensation these
OL,7,Fpeople want, it is accountability.
OL,8,FWhen we visited the area, residents
OL,9,Ftold us they warned the mining
OL,10,Fcompanies that the dam wasn't secure
OL,11,Fbut claim they prioritised profit over
OL,12,Fsafety.
OL,14,FPriscila Monteiro told us: "The
OL,15,Fresidents used to talk and ask if the
OL,16,Fdam was safe, if there was any danger
OL,17,Fof it breaking. They used to always
OL,18,Fsay no, that we were safe.
OL,26,@kD@[tpvD@\OU
