OL,3,C'We lost everything': Fundao Dam burst
OL,4,Csurvivors are fighting for justice
OL,6,F"We always used to listen to that. If
OL,7,Fanything (wasn't safe) we thought
OL,8,FSamarco would let us know. Someone
OL,9,Fwould always ask how the dam was at
OL,10,F(residents) meetings. They'd say it
OL,11,Fwas safe and everything was alright.
OL,12,FHow was everything alright when this
OL,13,Fhappened?"
OL,15,F"I couldn't speak because my throat
OL,16,Fwas full of mud," Priscila said.
OL,18,FThere are almost 700,000 claimants in
OL,19,Fthe lawsuit against the parent
OL,20,Fcompanies Vale and BHP and the case
OL,21,Fwill be heard at the High Court.
