OL,3,C'We lost everything': Fundao Dam burst
OL,4,Csurvivors are fighting for justice
OL,6,FIt will be the biggest group claim in
OL,7,FEnglish legal history. Largely because
OL,8,Fthis disaster stretched far beyond
OL,9,FBento Rodrigues.
OL,11,FWe travelled over 200 miles from
OL,12,FBento, along the River Doce to visit
OL,13,Fthe indigenous Krenak community. For
OL,14,Fcenturies, they co-existed with the
OL,15,FRiver Doce. They relied on it to feed
OL,16,Ftheir families, for fresh water and to
OL,17,Fmake a living. But above all they say
OL,18,Fthe river was sacred. But no more.
OL,26,@kD@[tp
