OL,3,C'We lost everything': Fundao Dam burst
OL,4,Csurvivors are fighting for justice
OL,6,FThe chief of the Krenak community
OL,7,FMarcello, told us: "We were always on
OL,8,Fthe river, we were fishing, hunting,
OL,9,Fplaying. Everything was on the river."
OL,11,FMarcello says their river was heavily
OL,12,Fpolluted when the mining waste reached
OL,13,Fthem in the days after the dam
OL,14,Fcollapse. As a result, they have lost
OL,15,Fnot only their river, but their
OL,16,Fidentity too.
OL,18,F"Everything was on the river. Then you
OL,19,Fsaw dead fish, some floating, some
OL,20,Fdying and struggling. It hurt and it
OL,21,Fstill hurts to this day."
