OL,3,C'We lost everything': Fundao Dam burst
OL,4,Csurvivors are fighting for justice
OL,6,FThe river is part of the identity of
OL,7,Fthe Krenak people. The Krenak people
OL,8,Fcall themselves Borum of Watu. And the
OL,9,FWatu is the river.
OL,11,FBHP says the water in the affected
OL,12,Fareas of the Doce River system is now
OL,13,Fback to the same quality as before the
OL,14,Fdam failure and that it is false to
OL,15,Fclaim the mud was toxic.
OL,17,FBut this is contested in other
OL,18,Fscientific reports.
