OL,3,C'We lost everything': Fundao Dam burst
OL,4,Csurvivors are fighting for justice
OL,6,FWe asked BHP to appear on On
OL,7,FAssignment, so we could share the
OL,8,Fstories of the people we met, but they
OL,9,Fdeclined. Instead they gave us a
OL,10,Fstatement, which included this:
OL,12,F"BHP, Samarco and Vale remain
OL,13,Fcommitted to providing reparations for
OL,14,Fthe people and environment affected by
OL,15,Fthe damage caused by the Fundao dam."
OL,17,FBoth BHP and Vale insist: "... this
OL,18,Fhas been done via the Brazilian
OL,19,Fjustice system and the continuing work
OL,20,Fof the Renova foundation."
